@node Main "Bipaire - Documentation"

                             'Bipaire' 1.06

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Bipaire " link play} is a Workbench game like 'Shangai', 'Dragon' or any
other games where you try to find pairs of matching tiles, but
unlike the oriental games, any visible tile can be choosen and
matched with another similar tile.

  When you find a pair of similar tiles, this pair is then
removed from the board, this may reveal part of tiles located
under. Continue to find all the remaining pairs until there are
no tiles left, or there are no pairs of similar tiles.

  When you complete a board, the game displays a new board and
the game continues. Can you complete all the boards that are
included in the game?

  Have fun!

